Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.25,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I'm gonna play with Saikawa at the park today.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Have fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:26.50,0:00:27.25,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.79,0:00:30.38,Default,T,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans for today, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.67,0:00:35.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,I guess spending a rare day off at home relaxing.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.26,0:00:36.84,Default,T,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.81,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'll do everything within my power as a maid to help you relax!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.35,0:00:43.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,Uh, could you just leave me be?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.44,Default,T,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.02,0:00:51.82,Default,T,0,0,0,,Be safe now.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.91,Default,T,0,0,0,,I hope the skies clear up.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.55,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.72,0:02:46.64,Default,S,0,0,0,,Shepherd's purse{, huh}?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.27,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Floriography?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.85,Default,S,0,0,0,,Yup. It's a book all about the language of flowers.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.81,Default,S,0,0,0,,Georgie let me borrow it.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.23,Default,S,0,0,0,,It's super interesting.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.49,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Saikawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.45,Default,S,0,0,0,,Shepherd's purse means...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.07,0:03:02.95,Default,S,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.83,Default,S,0,0,0,,"I offer my everything to you"?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.58,Default,S,0,0,0,,My everything...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.25,Default,S,0,0,0,,To you, Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.92,0:03:15.80,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,"My everything"?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.23,Default,T,0,0,0,,Have some, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sure. Thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.49,Default,T,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, it's good.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.21,0:03:56.38,Default,T,0,0,0,,I've been making adjustments to the flavor \Nand temperature based on your mood.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.51,Default,K,0,0,0,,You dragons can do some cool stuff.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.47,Default,T,0,0,0,,Being a dragon has nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.76,Default,T,0,0,0,,This is all me!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.93,Default,T,0,0,0,,I should go shopping soon.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.22,0:04:13.23,Default,T,0,0,0,,What should we have for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,Rice omelettes.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.49,Default,T,0,0,0,,Sounds good. Let's go with that!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.61,Default,K,0,0,0,,Nothing weird today, okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.45,Default,T,0,0,0,,Your wish is my command!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.37,Default,T,0,0,0,,All right, see you soon.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.58,Default,K,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.88,Default,T,0,0,0,,Rice omelette, rice omelette!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.67,Default - Italic,TV,0,0,0,,That's a short lifespan.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.51,0:04:45.72,Default - Italic,Man,0,0,0,,It is. A mouse has an expected lifespan of \Naround twelve to eighteen months, for instance.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.22,Default - Italic,Woman,0,0,0,,How sad!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.14,Default - Italic,Man,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.14,0:04:53.23,Default - Italic,Man,0,0,0,,All life has its own perception of time, \Nand to base it on human standards...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.98,Default,D,0,0,0,,How long do you plan to keep this up?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.90,0:05:03.19,Default,T,0,0,0,,Are you... me?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.19,0:05:06.74,Default,D,0,0,0,,Correct. I am the doubt in your mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.83,Default,D,0,0,0,,Do not avert your eyes.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.29,Default,D,0,0,0,,Do not deceive yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.04,Default,D,0,0,0,,I ask you again.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.17,Default,D,0,0,0,,How long do you plan to keep this up?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.26,0:05:35.10,Default,T,0,0,0,,All I want is to enjoy my time together with Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.85,Default,D,0,0,0,,For how long, though?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.52,0:05:42.78,Default,D,0,0,0,,You know it in your heart that you have to go back someday.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.19,Default,T,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.24,Default,T,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.24,0:05:50.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm Miss Kobayashi's maid.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.41,Default,D,0,0,0,,No, you are a dragon.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.12,Default,T,0,0,0,,What if you have an obligation to return?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.88,Default,T,0,0,0,,What if the war worsens over there?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.38,Default,T,0,0,0,,What if you start to thirst for blood?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.42,Default,T,0,0,0,,And what if Miss Kobayashi...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.48,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.44,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.81,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,My home...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.58,Default,T,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.83,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You must realize why I'm here.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.08,0:06:44.09,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You're coming back with me, Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.09,0:06:47.01,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You do not belong here.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.86,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Lady Tohru?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.49,Default,K,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.32,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru still isn't back.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.58,Default,K,0,0,0,,Just where did she go shopping?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.71,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Lady Tohru went home.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.17,Default,K,0,0,0,,Like I said, she's still—
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.17,0:07:23.92,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,She went {\i1}home{\i0}.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.05,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,To the other world.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.34,0:07:33.39,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,The Emperor of Demise, Lady Tohru's father, \Nmust've come to pick her up.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.32,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,She probably won't come back to this world.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.03,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Can't defy the Emperor of Demise.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.41,0:07:53.70,Default,K,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.84,Default,K,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.61,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wake up, Kanna! You'll be late!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.90,Default,K,0,0,0,,Shoot, this is bad!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,Whoa, almost forgot!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yikes...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.09,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.13,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.13,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.55,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.55,0:08:56.89,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.89,0:08:57.55,Default,K,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, Yamashita.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.68,Default,Y,0,0,0,,About that bug...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.81,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll fix it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.81,0:09:04.69,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.23,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.44,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Something happen?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.66,0:09:19.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru went back to the other world.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.46,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.17,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.64,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,Let's have dinner right away.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.02,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.41,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.92,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Working overtime until this late.{meh}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,Kanna's sleeping over at Saikawa's place tonight.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.00,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.17,0:10:59.38,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Want to hit the bar once we're done?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,I think I'll pass tonight.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.85,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Got it. Some other time.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.64,0:11:13.77,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,Lady Kanna, milady, good night.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.61,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:18.28,0:11:21.07,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong, Kanna?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.46,Default,L,0,0,0,,Tohru...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.31,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:15.38,0:12:20.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,If I'd seen this coming, \NI would've told her the rice omelette was good.{meh}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.10,Default,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi, it's me!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.23,Default,T,0,0,0,,It's me, Tohru!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.83,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm home, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.58,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I can't get in like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.13,Default,T,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,Didn't you go back home? To the other world?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.35,Default,T,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.02,Default,T,0,0,0,,But I'm back now.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.57,Default,T,0,0,0,,This feels kind of awkward.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.73,0:13:21.53,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:26.07,0:13:29.03,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm home, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.79,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah. Welcome back, Toh—
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.17,0:13:38.88,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.93,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.43,Default,T,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.43,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,That's her...?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.93,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Why did you return without permission{on your own}?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.68,0:13:56.31,Default,T,0,0,0,,I really want to stay here.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:56.31,0:13:56.94,Default,T,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:56.94,0:13:57.81,Default,Father,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:59.35,0:14:04.82,Default,Father,0,0,0,,I told you. We are forbidden \Nfrom interfering in this world's affairs.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.65,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You will come back home with me.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.83,Default,Father,0,0,0,,What you want is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:18.25,0:14:22.00,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You understand that this world \Nis off limits, do you not?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.00,0:14:26.17,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You mustn't disrupt it out of some selfish desire.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.76,Default,T,0,0,0,,I want to stay here.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.26,Default,T,0,0,0,,This is my home.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.06,0:14:38.02,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Can you live an unremarkable life as a human?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.15,Default,Father,0,0,0,,It will slowly eat away at you.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.40,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Have you not realized this?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.45,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Come home, Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.33,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Before you get hurt.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.50,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Should I say something here?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.50,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Should I call him out for being unfair?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.01,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,But I can't just butt in on \Na conversation between family.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:07.59,0:15:10.26,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,I should respect Tohru's decision.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:10.63,0:15:11.51,Default,T,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:19.02,0:15:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.52,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Choose your words carefully.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:25.82,0:15:29.86,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Depending on what you say, \Nyou might be erased from this world.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.29,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm home, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.26,Default,Father,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru said she doesn't want to go back!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.98,Default,F,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:02.52,0:16:05.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,You can't interfere with this world, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,That means you can't kill me.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.99,Default,Father,0,0,0,,But I can leave you at death's door.{But I can do anything short of killing you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:09.99,0:16:12.49,Default,K,0,0,0,,That won't change my mind!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.49,0:16:18.24,Default,Father,0,0,0,,The rules of the universe mustn't be broken.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.79,0:16:24.63,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Dragons are supposed to uphold its integrity.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.13,Default,Father,0,0,0,,If others learned of one living here, \Nthey might follow it here.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:28.13,0:16:33.38,Default,Father,0,0,0,,It might not be a problem yet, but eventually, someone could come here plotting an invasion.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.64,Default,Father,0,0,0,,What then?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:35.64,0:16:38.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,That wouldn't be Tohru's fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.89,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're just twisting this into her responsibility!{She's not responsible for the actions of others!}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.89,Default,Father,0,0,0,,What I said is entirely possible.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,Who gives a damn?!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.73,0:16:49.32,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Why are you so fixated on Tohru?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.86,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Are you in love with her?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.74,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You, a mere human? Preposterous.{Unbelievable.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:54.74,0:16:57.53,Default,K,0,0,0,,Really? But she's such a great girl.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:57.53,0:16:59.70,Default,Father,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly aware of that.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,She's cheery and fun to be around.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.75,Default,K,0,0,0,,Her face clouds over sometimes,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,but she hides it with a smile.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.84,Default,K,0,0,0,,And, you know, she's my maid!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.34,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're not taking my maid anywhere!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:16.68,0:17:17.93,Default,K,0,0,0,,She's mine!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.47,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You overstep—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.48,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.48,0:17:28.23,Default,Father,0,0,0,,This place is too constrained. Follow me.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:49.04,0:17:52.88,Default,Father,0,0,0,,This is the first time you've ever dared to defy me.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.51,Default,T,0,0,0,,I want to choose where I belong myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:57.34,0:18:01.05,Default,T,0,0,0,,I respect and admire you, Father.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.93,Default,T,0,0,0,,But only as a dragon.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:03.93,0:18:06.27,Default,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi is my...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:08.06,0:18:08.85,Default,T,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.15,Default,T,0,0,0,,She is my light!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.03,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You know nothing.{You don't understand a thing.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.36,Default,T,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.87,Default,Father,0,0,0,,If you bare your fangs at me, \NI shall show you no mercy.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.01,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Come back home, foolish daughter!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.84,Default,T,0,0,0,,I will not!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.14,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Living with a human is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:43.39,0:18:45.39,Default,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi is special!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.44,Default,Father,0,0,0,,This is your final warning.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.57,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Come home.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.82,Default,T,0,0,0,,I will not!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.69,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You stubborn fool!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.37,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.04,Default,T,0,0,0,,Kanna! Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why are you fighting? You're father and daughter!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.09,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Stay out of this, human.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:18.09,0:19:21.80,Default,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi, I'm sorry, \Nbut please stay away for now.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.81,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why are dragons all like this?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:25.22,0:19:28.93,Default,K,0,0,0,,You gotta make a compromise, \Nor you won't get anywhere!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.48,Default,Father,0,0,0,,What is your point?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm saying you're jumping to extremes.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.31,Default,K,0,0,0,,I can never understand this side of you guys.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:34.31,0:19:39.07,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Of course. Humans and dragons \Nwill never see eye to eye.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.07,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,Knowing how different you are is just the start line.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:45.58,0:19:50.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,You run laps from there and keep opening or closing the distance.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:50.41,0:19:54.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,You'll gradually find things you like and learn to respect each other.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:55.09,0:19:57.09,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Respect, you say?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,You can learn to build trust and bonds, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:05.76,0:20:09.60,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Do you genuinely believe you can coexist?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.10,Default,K,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.60,Default,K,0,0,0,,We've been coexisting for ages now.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.11,Default,K,0,0,0,,The question is whether we can believe it'll last.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,And I believe.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,Try having some faith in your daughter!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.92,Default,Father,0,0,0,,I will not accept this.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:38.92,0:20:44.89,Default,Father,0,0,0,,A mere human, who can't even live long enough to stay by her side?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.89,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Tohru,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.39,Default,Father,0,0,0,,you truly are a foolish daughter.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sorry for acting of my own accord there.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.08,Default,T,0,0,0,,How can I ever repay you for this?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:16.54,0:21:17.46,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.00,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'll give you everything!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.67,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's too much.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:40.11,0:21:41.90,Default,K,0,0,15,,Morning, Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.19,Default,T,0,0,15,,Good morning, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:44.19,0:21:45.99,Default,Kanna,0,0,15,,Lady Tohru, good morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.53,Default,T,0,0,15,,Morning, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:47.78,0:21:50.03,Default,Takiya,0,0,15,,I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:50.03,0:21:51.45,Default,Fafnir,0,0,15,,We're out of conditioner.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:51.45,0:21:53.41,Default,Takiya,0,0,15,,Okay, I'll buy more.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.20,Default,Fafnir,0,0,15,,Also...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.16,Default,Takiya,0,0,15,,8 o'clock, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:56.46,0:21:57.92,Default,Takiya,0,0,15,,I know.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:59.71,0:22:02.17,Default,S,0,0,15,,Kanna said she would come hang out again today.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:02.50,0:22:05.42,Default,Georgie,0,0,15,,I'll ready some chocolate, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:06.09,0:22:07.38,Default,S,0,0,15,,Chocolate?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:12.31,0:22:14.10,Default,L,0,0,15,,Have a good day, Shouta.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:14.10,0:22:16.10,Default,Shouta,0,0,15,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:16.94,0:22:19.69,Default,Clerk,0,0,15,,Would you like to try our new waffle?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:20.02,0:22:22.11,Default,Clerk,0,0,15,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:23.36,0:22:24.07,Default,K,0,0,15,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:24.07,0:22:25.19,Default,T,0,0,15,,Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:25.19,0:22:27.99,Default,K,0,0,15,,{\q2}It's been a while, so I might head back home for a bit.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:27.99,0:22:29.53,Default,T,0,0,15,,Oh, that sounds good.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:29.53,0:22:31.07,Default,T,0,0,15,,You really should go.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:31.62,0:22:33.45,Default,K,0,0,15,,Wanna come with me?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:04.07,0:23:07.82,Default - Italic,T,0,0,15,,I can't spend my whole life with Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:08.19,0:23:11.24,Default - Italic,T,0,0,15,,I know we'll have to part ways someday.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:15.83,0:23:21.83,Default - Italic,T,0,0,15,,{\q2}Even so, I'll never feel I was better off not meeting her.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:24.79,0:23:28.63,Default - Italic,T,0,0,15,,I'll simply treasure the time we have together.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:35.76,0:23:38.93,Default,K,0,0,15,,{\t(1700,3157,\c&H000000&)}I'm home!
