Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.39,0:01:30.35,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I only made one tiny-winey mistake
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.35,0:01:34.06,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(210,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}and now I'm at a ta-la-la ta-la-ta total loss
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.06,0:01:35.56,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Why now of all times
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.56,0:01:37.36,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.36,0:01:40.90,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.90,0:01:43.15,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}with no choice but to sing along
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.15,0:01:46.49,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}That's just how it is at first,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.49,0:01:50.16,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}feeling like you're not in control
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.71,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}But if you open up and listen...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.71,0:01:58.84,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(180,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.59,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}(Anywhere is fine!)
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.59,0:02:07.47,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,160)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I have the courage to become your wings
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.47,0:02:11.02,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I'll take on the world without any fear
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.02,0:02:14.94,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(220,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}as long as I feel this magic
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.94,0:02:21.73,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.61,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(170,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}wrapped up together in this moment
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.61,0:02:27.28,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}We communicate on different levels,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.28,0:02:29.16,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}but it doesn't bother me one bit
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.16,0:02:31.58,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,240)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}so long as this peace lasts forevermore
