Comment: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:37.36,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Comment: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:40.90,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Comment: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:43.15,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}with no choice but to sing along
Comment: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:46.49,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}That's just how it is at first,
Comment: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:50.16,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}feeling like you're not in control
Comment: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.71,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}But if you open up and listen...
Comment: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:58.84,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Comment: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.59,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}(Anywhere is fine!)
Comment: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:07.47,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I have the courage to become your wings
Comment: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:11.02,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I'll take on the world without any fear
Comment: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:14.94,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}as long as I feel this magic
Comment: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:21.73,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Comment: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.61,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}wrapped up together in this moment
Comment: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:27.28,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}We communicate on different levels,
Comment: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:29.16,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}but it doesn't bother me one bit
Comment: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:31.58,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}so long as this peace lasts forevermore